room_title: Escape room "Fort Ord Lockdown" by Escape Room Salinas in Salinas
room_description: Today is your last day of basic training. It’s been 4 long months of grueling training. Physically and mentally you and your squad are drained. This is your final test. You’ve come this far, now its time to see what you’re made of. You will have 60 minutes to find the key and escape. Your time starts, now
